data.description: 100% financing USDA Rural Housing Loan for eligible Buyer.  Single level living with this ranch style home located in established non HOA neighborhood.  Large .88 acre lot has privacy for backyard enjoyment and area with trees remains in back.   Covered patio complete with fun evening lighting and mature landscaping are some of the exterior features of this low maintenance vinyl sided home.   Front lawn leads to a covered porch area as you enter the home. Large living room w/ soaring ceiling and decorative wood beam. Recent updates include laminate flooring and both bathrooms with new vanities and fixtures.   Ceramic tiled kitchen with eat in area is open space and all its' appliances will remain.   Laundry space located in garage at entry into kitchen. Master suite features double closet and full bathroom with tub/shower.  Location is convenient to grocery, schools and Lake Hartwell and its many public access areas and boat launches. Interstate access, restaurants and even ever growing downtown Anderson are all a short ride away.
